House of Food - Season 1, Episode 5




Big Beef

Chris calls a House meeting to let everyone know that Harrison wants to speak to them all. Some revolt, saying they do not want to here his apology and what he is going to say to them and walk out of the room. Only 4 of the cast remain on the couch just to hear what he has to say.




Original Air Date: 28-Apr-2014
